<input [pattern]="page.usernamePattern" formControlName = "username" type="text" style="width: 98%; height:100% ; border: 2px solid gray;
    border-radius: 20px; font-size: 18px; background-color: #80808014; padding-left: 6px">

Your username must be between 8 - 30 characters long. It must contain:
  • Numbers (0 - 9)
  • Lower case (a - z)
  • Upper case (A - Z)
  • Special characters (@)
You cannot use an ID number as a username.
